name: Matabolong's Avocado Journal 006
description: After walking for a while, the scenery starts to change. The green turns into purplish red. The air felt thick and damp. Left and right there's a lot of mushrooms. I can feel the spores starts to seep into my body. My leg felt light, everything looks like fun and jasd.. aiddd... saias .ladsn n..ll lrop oo...flowers??..?
